1st cycle: m1 = as instruction in P2; w(P1) = 0; start incrementer
2nd Cycle: m1 = 0, m2 = 0 couter=000(P2)
3rd Cylce: m1 = 1, m2 = 1 couter=001(P2)

in same cycle w(P1) = 1
